gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 124, Grizzlies 93
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Grizzlies, 124-93. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded 23 points (5-7 3PT FG) and six assists for the Thunder, while Cason Wallace added a career-high 22 points (4-6 3PT FG) in the victory. GG Jackson tallied a career-high 30 points, along with six rebounds for the Grizzlies in the losing effort. The Thunder are on a three-game win streak as they improve to 45-19 on the season, while the Grizzlies fall to 22-43.
